posts.title: Email Marketing Do’s And Don’ts Web Design New York Companies Must Follow
posts.text:
By Arthur Williams Are you struggling with getting in touch with your target audience? If so, there’s a good chance that you haven’t taken advantage of email marketing. If your strategy is crafted well, you will see web design New York success of the highest level. After all, your website can make or break future sales. For a better understanding of how email marketing should be carried out, consider the following do’s & don’ts. DO exhibit creativity with your campaigns. Email marketing, as the likes of Avatar New York will tell you, hinges on creativity. It’s your best interest to craft each email so that it’s unique, whether it’s in terms of images used, the specific content being displayed, or what have you. Uniqueness is what helps the campaigns in question stand out. No one that offers web design New York services will be able to disagree.
DON’T group your audience into a box. Email marketing should be versatile in terms of who’s being messaged. Not everyone has the same interests and goals, which means that modifying your campaigns ever so slightly is important. By focusing on user feedback, you’ll have a better understanding of where to take your campaigns moving forward. This is another way to go about email marketing of the highest quality.
DO make unsubscribing as painless as possible. One of the ways to do this – and this is relatively common – is by including a small link in the footer of your newsletter. This can be used in order for a subscriber to opt out of future newsletters. While this implementation seems like a no-brainer, it can go a long way in establishing your email marketing campaign as credible. A number of Internet marketing companies can say the same.
DON’T overlook the importance of testing emails. Just because you have a strong newsletter doesn’t necessarily mean that it will be at the forefront of one’s inbox. As a matter of fact, if you’re not careful, the emails that you send could land into several spam folders. This is a problem, mainly because it means fewer people will open the emails you’ve spent considerable time on. By using your own smaller email accounts for testing, you’ll have a better understanding of how your campaigns will perform in the future.

thread.title_full: 비철금속, 경기회복·4차 산업혁명 타고 더 오른다…펀드도 눈돌릴 만 : 네이버 뉴스

posts.author: 한국경제 | 네이버 뉴스
posts.title: 비철금속, 경기회복·4차 산업혁명 타고 더 오른다…펀드도 눈돌릴 만 뉴스
posts.text:
글로벌 경기 회복과 함께 4차 산업혁명의 시대가 도래하면서 원자재 가격이 들썩이고 있다. 특히 구리 니켈 등 비철금속의 강세는 내년에도 이어질 전망이어서 관련 기업과 펀드에 대한 시장의 관심이 커지고 있다.
김형렬 교보증권 연구원은 7일 "원자재 가격이 추세적인 상승 조짐을 보이면서 내년 세계경제와 주식시장에 대한 기대감을 높이고 있다"고 밝혔다.
원자재 상품은 크게 금 은 등 귀금속과 철광석 비철금속 등 산업금속, 원유 천연가스 등 에너지, 밀 콩 옥수수 등 곡물 시장으로 분류된다. 미국을 필두로 글로벌 경기가 본격적인 회복 국면에 진입하면서 원유와 귀금속, 산업금속의 상승세가 두드러지고 있다.
문남중 대신증권 연구원도 금리 인상 가능성이 높은 12월 미국 연방공개시장위원회(FOMC)를 앞두고 달러화 강세 압력이 높아지더라도 원자재 가격의 강세는 지속될 것으로 봤다. 공급부담이 완화된 가운데 하반기부터 수요 개선이 나타나고 있다는 분석에서다.
문 연구원은 "특히 비철금속의 경우 중국의 환경규제 강화, 전기차 시장 확대에 따른 희귀금속 수요 증가로 강세가 지속될 전망"이라고 설명했다.
비철금속은 4차 산업혁명의 중심에 있는 전기차시장이 가파르게 성장하면서 상승세를 나타내고 있다. 신한금융투자에 따르면 올해 철광석을 제외한 비철금속 가격은 연초 대비 10~30%나 올랐다.
비철금속 가운데 연초 대비 23% 오른 구리는 수요가 끌어주고 공급이 밀어주는 강세 국면이 지속, 내년에는 올해보다 약 20% 더 오를 것이라는 전망이다. 알루미늄, 니켈의 경우 초과 수요 상태가 지속되며 가격이 추가 상승할 것으로 보인다.
장밋빛 전망이 잇따르면서 연초 후 비철금속 관련 펀드에는 자금이 꾸준히 유입되고 있다. 한국펀드평가펀드스퀘어에 따르면 미래에셋운용의 '미래에셋로저스Commodity인덱스특별자산자(일반상품-파생)C-B', 블랙록자산운용의 '블랙록월드광업주[자](주식-재간접)(H)(A)'에는 각각 158억원, 157억원의 자금이 유입됐다.
수익률도 긍정적이다. '삼성KODEX구리선물(H)특별자산상장지수(구리-파생)'과 '미래에셋TIGER금속선물특별자산상장지수투자신탁[금속-파생형]'는 연초 후 20%가 넘는 수익률을 기록했다. 각각 21.4%, 21.53%였다. 두 펀드는 최근 석 달간에만 각각 7.85%, 10.47%의 수익률을 달성했다.

posts.text: 부산 유통가, 수능 특수를 잡아라 파이낸셜뉴스 입력 :2017.11.07 17:59 수정 : 2017.11.07 17:59 인쇄 수험생들의 개성을 중시한 미니 게임기, 저가형 드론 등 다양한 이색상품 출시 봇물 "선배님들 수능대박 기원합니다" 부산 사상구 주례여자고등학교 1학년 학생 250여명이 7일 오전 학교 운동장에서 수능을 앞둔 3학년 언니들을 위해 수능대박 기원 '플래시몹 응원'을 펼치고 있다. 이날 1학년 학생들은 걸그룹 트와이스의 'cheer up'과 소녀시대의 '힘내' 음악에 맞춰 2주 동안 갈고 닦은 춤을 선보였다. 3학년 학생들은 교실 창문을 통해 후배들의 공연을 관람하고 감사의 마음을 담아 박수를 보냈다. 7일 부산 부전동 롯데백화점 부산본점 7층 스타일 온에어 플러스 매장에서 수능을 마친 수험생들을 위한 이색 선물들을 선보이고 있는 가운데 고객들이 미니 게임기를 사용해보고 있다. 오는 16일 치러지는 2018년 대입수학능력시험(수능)을 앞두고 부산지역 유통가가 수능 특수 잡기에 들어갔다. 7일 부산 유통가에 따르면 그동안은 수험생을 위한 선물이 시험 전 엿, 떡, 초콜릿으로 응원의 마음을 전하는 것이 대표적이었다면, 이제는 시험이 끝난 뒤 수험생들이 평소 원하던 것이나 이색상품을 선물하는 경우가 늘고 있는 추세다. 실제로 이러한 트렌드에 맞춰 유통업계들은 수능을 마친 수험생을 위한 다양한 이색상품들을 출시하고 있다. 부산 부전동 롯데백화점 부산본점의 7층 스타일 온에어 플러스 매장에서는 실제로 옛날 오락실에 있던 게임기를 그대로 축소한 형태의 '미니 게임기'를 선보이고 있다. 이 미니 게임기는 200여 종류가 넘는 게임이 내장돼 있다. 업계는 수능을 마친 수험생들에게 옛 추억과 즐거움을 동시에 선사하며 큰 인기를 얻을 것으로 기대하고 있다. 롯데 부산본점 6층 드론(무인항공기) 매장에는 5만원 이하의 저가형 드론 세트가 다양하게 입고 돼 수능을 마친 수험생을 위한 선물 문의가 이어지고 있다고 전했다. 롯데 부산본점 임점택 영스트리트 팀장은 "획일적이던 수능 선물에서 벗어나 수험생만의 개성을 중시한 이색 선물을 찾는 경우가 점차 늘고 있다"며 "남자 수험생을 위한 선물로는 마블 캐릭터로 만들어진 피규어 또는 드론과 게임기 등이, 여자 수험생의 경우에는 라인프렌즈 캐릭터가 그려진 블루투스 스피커, 주문 제작형 마카롱 등이 인기가 있다"고 설명했다. 그러나 여전히 수능 이전인 만큼, 시험을 위한 실용적인 상품들도 인기를 끌고 있다. 부산 해운대 우동의 신세계 센텀시티 몰 지하2층 반디앤루니스에서는 낮잠쿠션, 시계, 엿, 초콜릿 등 수능 고득점을 기원하는 다양한 응원 상품을 판매하고 있다. 또 신세계 센텀시티 백화점 내 베이커리 브랜드 '더 메나쥬리'에서는 수능 합격을 기원하는 콘셉트의 케이크 '잘 풀리는 수능'을 선보이고 있다. 이 케이크는 두루마리 휴지 모양으로 만들어 '문제를 술술 풀라'는 의미를 담았다. 이와 함께 신세계 센텀시티 몰 한식뷔페 '올반'에서는 수능 당일인 오는 16일부터 30일까지 수험표를 소지한 수험생을 대상으로 30% 할인 이벤트도 실시한다. 강수련 기자

posts.author: وكالة المساء نيوز الدولية (noreply@blogger.com)
posts.title: طاولة الصناعة تمثل العراق في البطولة العربية
posts.text:
المساء نيوز / ابراهيم محمد 

وصل وفد نادي الصناعة الرياضي بكرة الطاولة، إلى  لبنان  للمشاركة في البطولة العربية ممثلا للعراق، ويضم الفريق ثلاث لاعبات ينافسن في البطولة.

وقال مدرب الفريق علي فاضل في حديث لوكالة المساء نيوز، إن "النادي سيكون ممثلا للعراق في منافسات البطولة العربية التي ستنطلق اليوم الثلاثاء، في لبنان بمشاركة واسعة من الأندية العربية".

وأضاف فاضل أن "وفد النادي وصل امس الاثنين، إلى لبنان وباشر بالتحضير للمباريات التي سخوضها في البطولة"، مشيرا إلى أن "ثلاث لاعبات سيمثلن الفريق في البطولة هن عفاف منذر وحنين هاشم ومينا حسن".

posts.title: Benefits Of Private Nurses Los Gatos
posts.text:
By Virginia Powell 

Patients with extreme and long ailments can get better assistance from a private medical practitioner who is specialized in home care. As opposed to reoccurring and costly hospital inpatient visits, home care experts offer a productive and inspiring chance to recover. The financial burden is also decreased by a huge margin. When you need private nurses Los Gatos is a lovely place to find services.

There are various ways in which a nurse offers support for a patient who is staying at home. The first is medical support. Good healthcare is not limited to hospitals only. Professionals can take their skills and experience to home care. A patient will get good personalized care and avoid the struggle of getting to hospitals. All you need is to hire an expert who is licensed and available for day to day care as well as emergencies.

Home care providers likewise offer support emotionally. With an ill relative at home there are many confounding feelings from the family members as well. It is better to have an expert nearby to comfort both the family and the patient. Specialists have presumably been involved in numerous comparative circumstances and they can give essential emotional support. You will dependably have somebody to hear you out and offer a shoulder.

A private nurse will also help you to adapt to the situation and provide therapy services. Albeit private home attendants are known to be efficient when the conditions are short term, they can also be hired for chronic and long-term illnesses. This includes disabilities, dementia and other conditions such as Parkinsons.

A good nurse will treat the initial problems associated with the chronic illnesses and then proceed to offer therapy for both the patient and the family. These techniques are aimed at helping you cope in the long run. Through the painful and difficult situations the expert will offer reassurance and hope.

The job of a private medical attendant goes beyond just the medical checks. By combining medicinal and emotional support with therapy a huge improvement is made on the patient. Family additionally profits from the therapy and diminished dissatisfaction that is found in healing facilities as well as many nursing homes.

Since home is the place patients feel most cherished and tended to, bring a nurse there results in the best possible care. Finding reputable professionals is easy when you have a working internet connection. Many home care providers have an online presence and you will find it easy to compare different services.

You can refer to registries to find the best home care providers. Ensure you hire a qualified nurse with a lot of experience in various fields. There are plenty of service providers who hire exemplary nurses and guarantee the best care possible. You can set up an appointment before hiring any professional. This will give you a chance to evaluate how good the services are before signing any contract. You need to confirm that your insurance company will pay some or all costs associated with home care.




About the Author:

You can find a summary of the reasons why you should hire private nurses Los Gatos area at http://www.privatenursesolutions.com right now.

posts.title: Beer sieht Chancen für Jamaika-Einigung bei 50:50 | HITRADIO RTL
posts.text:
Die Generalsekretärin der FDP, Nicola Beer, der Vorsitzende Christian Lindner (M) und der stellvertretende Bundesvorsitzende Wolfgang Kubicki in Berlin. Foto: Wolfgang Kumm Beer sieht Chancen für Jamaika-Einigung bei 50:50 Zuletzt aktualisiert: 07.11.2017 | 08:12 Uhr Autor: 
Berlin (dpa) - Unmittelbar vor Beginn der zweiten Phase der Jamaikasondierungen hat FDP-Generalsekretärin Nicola Beer die Chancen einer Einigung erneut mit 50:50 bewertet. «Wir streben erst mal keine Neuwahlen an», sagte sie im Radioprogramm SWR Aktuell am Dienstagmorgen. 
Zugleich betonte Beer, dass die FDP eine andere Politik machen wolle als die große Koalition: «Wenn das nicht möglich ist, weil die anderen Gesprächspartner nicht mutig genug für einen Politikwechsel sind, dann gehen wir lieber in Neuwahlen, als dass wir uns verbiegen lassen.» 
Die FDP wolle bei den Sondierungen eine Zielperspektive mit CDU, CSU und Grünen verhandeln, «wo wir dieses Land in 5, 10 oder 15 Jahren hinführen wollen», betonte die FDP-Politikerin. Das bedeute für die FDP sowohl ein Einwanderungsgesetz als auch eine bessere Ausstattung bei Polizei und Justiz. 
Die Sondierungen von CDU, CSU, FDP und Grünen für eine Jamaika-Koalition gehen am Dienstag in die entscheidende zweite Phase. Bis Mitte November wollen die Unterhändler eine relativ klare Vereinbarung zustande bringen, auf deren Basis dann Ende des Monats - nach einem Parteitag der Grünen am 25. November - Koalitionsverhandlungen beginnen sollen.

posts.author: Claire McGarry
posts.title: Daily Gospel Reflection for November 7, 2017
posts.text:
You are at: Home »   » Daily Gospel Reflection for November 7, 2017 Daily Gospel Reflection for November 7, 2017 
Today’s Gospel: Luke 14:15-24 
We’ve all done it: left an event early to beat the traffic, only to learn later we missed the best part. The finale at the fireworks show turned out to be twice as good as ever before. Our losing sports team made a last minute play that made sports history, securing a win at the bottom of the ninth. The band we went to see did an unprecedented encore, playing the song we waited all night to hear. 
The next day, when we hear the news, we kick ourselves. We were there! Why did we leave? If only we hadn’t prioritized getting on the road, over what brought us there in the first place. Realizing our mistake, we’d gladly spend two hours in traffic for the chance to experience what we missed. 
In this scripture passage, each of the invited guests prioritizes something else over the banquet, and asks to be excused before the dinner is even served. The host goes into a rage and declares they will never taste his dinner. 
We are all invited to a similar banquet, the banquet of discipleship in Christ. We don’t have to earn a seat at the table. Jesus did that for us. 
However, we can’t bail out early. We have to stay the course, for the duration. We can’t just leave faith behind when things get tough and we experience our own personal traffic jam. Worse yet, we can’t walk away, and towards something else that looks better, seems more important, or feels easier. If we do, we won’t just miss out on a great finale, a history-making sports turnaround, or the encore of a lifetime. We’ll miss out on the whole purpose we were put on this earth in the first place: to experience the kingdom of God.

thread.section_title: Tagebuch eines Landpfarrers

posts.author: fentzloff
posts.text: Zu Arno Schmidt. Hohn und Verachtung können nicht gründlich genug ausgegossen werden, sofern der Gott der Kirche ins Visier gerät aufklärerischen, schriftstellerischen Bewußtseins. Mit Dreizack, mit jeder Art von Stichwaffen, denkbar differenziertester Bewaffnung überhaupt, wird auf ein vermeintlich Totes lustvoll eingestochen. Kirchenkritik ist oft Leichenschändung. Im Kelch des Denkens schäumt ein Geist des Hasses, ein tiefes Verletztsein (man weiß nicht woher). Nach Jahrhunderten theologiekritischen Denkens nichts Neues. Manchem verschafft es immer noch Befriedigung (und: Man findet ja immer Gründe, abfällig über das zu sprechen, was einem als Kirche zuweilen vor Augen tritt, was Kirche zu sein beansprucht, es aber nicht ist). Indes wir vor der Geburt einer neuen Kirche unmittelbar stehen. Ich teile die Überzeugung, daß die Frage nach der Kirche als eine der wesentlichen zukünftig sich erweisen wird. Das XXI. Jahrhundert sucht nach Notizen, die ein anderes und neues Bild entwerfen, sich auf die (geglaubte wie erfahrene) Christusgegenwart beziehen, das Wunderbare (welches gegenwärtig lebt im Exil der Dichtkunst), neu beschwören, verehren, ins Herz schließen. Ohne Kirche (jesuanisch ausgeleuchtete) verarmte unser Geschlecht auf grausame Art und Weise. Geheimnisvolle Pfade der Poesie, Spaziergänge am Rande der armen Wohnsiedlungen, würden nicht mehr stattfinden. Das Denken wäre tot; mausetot. Jean Paul und Herder und Goethe und Hölderlin – wären sie ohne den unterirdischen Gesang der Jahrhunderte jemals erwacht aus Sprachlosigkeit, hätten sie ihr Zeugnis sagen können – ohne das schöne Wort ›Kirche‹? In ihren Werken finden wir auf jeder Seite ein Suchen nach dem, was Kirche sei. Ich schreibe unbeirrt seit jeher an Notizen zu einer Theologie des XXI. Jahrhunderts. Nun, Arno Schmidts der Kirche zum Fraß vorgeworfener Spott hat mich nie davon abgehalten, seinem Werk mich zu widmen. Das Großereignis besonders in »Zettel’s Traum«: Auf den schwer entzifferbaren Seiten wird die Sprache als solche zu Gott. Die Sprache ist ein Offenbares und Verborgenes zugleich. Der Sprachkörper muß ganz neu vermessen, abgetastet, behutsamst zum Klingen gebracht werden. Noch ist nichts oder sehr wenig nur gesagt worden. Arno Schmidt ist unterwegs, Sprache ganz neu und anders aus der Taufe zu heben. Gerade im umgangssprachlichen Terrain tun jene Stollen sich auf, durch welche man hinuntersteigen und weitergraben kann. Ein mühseliges Unterfangen. Es braucht mehr als Geduld. Es gleicht die Lektüre Schmidt’scher Spätwerke dem Sortieren von Briefmarken unter der Lupe. Die einfachste und vermeintlich selbstverständlichste Aussage zersplittert unterm theopoetischen Zugriff des Bargfelder Meisters. Man muß die Splitter zusammensuchen und neu zusammensetzen, daß eine ganz andere Welt entsteht (›aufersteht‹); das Kaffeetassen-Anfassen etwa (entschieden der Joyce’schen Intention in »Finnegans Wake« entsprechend) einstimmt in den ersten hohen Gesang der Schöpfung zur Stunde einer ersten Morgenfrühe des anders geschauten und anders gedeuteten Kosmos. Im prophetischen Sinne sind zwei Schriftsteller für unsere Zeit (als in unsere Not hineinsprechende Autoren) von allergrößter Bedeutung: Ich nenne ihre Namen, wissend, daß die Partisanen des jeweiligen Lagers im Grab sich umdrehen würden, bzw. sofern sie in dieser Welt noch stehen, zum Sich-Totlachen angehalten wären, wüßten sie die beiden Namen in einem Atemzug ausgeprochen ––– ich nenne die Namen zweier Erzfeinde, die gerade als Einheit von Bedeutung mir erscheinen: Arno Schmidt und Ernst Jünger. Schmidt der Sprachprophet; Jünger der Schauende und Wissende. Schmidt – vergleichsweise früh, Jünger mit über hundert Jahren gestorben; Schmidt ein Sprachmagier, Jünger (meiner bescheidenen Betrachtungsweise entsprechend) der Einzige, der über das Kommende (nach Hölderlin und Nietzsche), über willkürliches Spekulieren der Straßenecke hinaus, etwas zu sagen weiß.
